      "text": "- create repositroy: workload8\n- create repository: terraform-modules\n- create repository: github-actions \n- upload alloydb module to terraform-modules\n  https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/cloud-foundation-fabric/tree/master/modules/alloydb#psc-instance\n- use alloydb module in workload8 (use PSC!)\n- setup github actions (use tms-workload as a base, change SA and WIF)\n  GCP config: workload identity federation\n  authentication to allow worklaod8 to access terraform-modules\n\n- later on we use the github-actions repo for all the workflows",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- create repositroy: workload8\n- create repository: terraform-modules\n- create repository: github-actions \n- upload alloydb module to terraform-modules\n  https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/cloud-foundation-fabric/tree/master/modules/alloydb#psc-instance\n- use alloydb module in workload8 (use PSC!)\n- setup github actions (use tms-workload as a base, change SA and WIF)\n  GCP config: workload identity federation\n  authentication to allow worklaod8 to access terraform-modules\n\n- later on we use the github-actions repo for all the workflows",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
