      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "versions.tf\n-> which versions to use\nterraform {\n  required_version = \">= 1.12.2\"\n  required_providers {\n    google = {\n      source  = \"hashicorp/google\"\n      version = \">= 7.6.0, < 8.0.0\" # tftest\n    }\n}",
