      "originalText": "Creating new workload repos\n- Settings\n  - Collaborators and Teams\n    - add people there\n  - General:\n    - enable: Automatically delete head branches \n  - Environments:\n    - Create: dev and prod\n      enable: Required reviewers and add reviewers\n  - Secrets and variables\n    - Create secret: SSH_KEY\n",
