      "text": "tms-alloydb-user\n- gcloud alloydb clusters describe adb-d-eu-bld01-clst --region=europe-west3\n-> manual wf -> Users are created with glcoud command (no tfstate)\n-> auto wf -> currently only in prj-cal-w-cicd-wl3-b213-53ad (WL3)\n   -> Project_id referenced in GitHub variables",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "tms-alloydb-user\n- gcloud alloydb clusters describe adb-d-eu-bld01-clst --region=europe-west3\n-> manual wf -> Users are created with glcoud command (no tfstate)\n-> auto wf -> currently only in prj-cal-w-cicd-wl3-b213-53ad (WL3)\n   -> Project_id referenced in GitHub variables",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
