      "updated": 1765977802997,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Set up user and Secrets for WL2 (extend tms-alloydb-secret-manager)\n1. Configure tms-alloydb-secret-manager\n- Test pipeline if it works\n- Test with pull request and check Terraform Plan\n2. Copy code from tms-alloyb-user to tms-alloydb-secrets-manager to create user\n- Copy user creation commands\n- Test user creation\n3. Test user creation in tms-alloydb-secrets-manager\n- Create pull request with new users",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Set up user and Secrets for WL2 (extend tms-alloydb-secret-manager)\n1. Configure tms-alloydb-secret-manager\n- Test pipeline if it works\n- Test with pull request and check Terraform Plan\n2. Copy code from tms-alloyb-user to tms-alloydb-secrets-manager to create user\n- Copy user creation commands\n- Test user creation\n3. Test user creation in tms-alloydb-secrets-manager\n- Create pull request with new users",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
