      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bMJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 854805746,
      "version": 646,
      "versionNonce": 1571091566,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1765812479154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Fixing error in Workflow for creating VMs:\n1. Add the Dev Network and Dev Subnet\n2. Creating a Feature Branch and commiting the changes there (vm-management.yml line 214)\n\nRon wants:\n1. Creating Random VM name ([d|t|p]-[A-Za-z0-9](5)). From this name create a new tfvars file with the code (line 103)\n1.1 Dynamicly listing all the created VMs in an other Workflow to delete them\nLater On\n2. Some way to stop the VM in the evening 8pm (https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/storage-data-transfer/save-money-by-stopping-and-starting-compute-engine-instances-on-schedule)\n3. Creating some alerts when the machine runs to long and is not accessed for 3 days",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fixing error in Workflow for creating VMs:\n1. Add the Dev Network and Dev Subnet\n2. Creating a Feature Branch and commiting the changes there (vm-management.yml line 214)\n\nRon wants:\n1. Creating Random VM name ([d|t|p]-[A-Za-z0-9](5)). From this name create a new tfvars file with the code (line 103)\n1.1 Dynamicly listing all the created VMs in an other Workflow to delete them\nLater On\n2. Some way to stop the VM in the evening 8pm (https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/storage-data-transfer/save-money-by-stopping-and-starting-compute-engine-instances-on-schedule)\n3. Creating some alerts when the machine runs to long and is not accessed for 3 days",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
